short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extension to set custom week number for Google calendar

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is an extension to set custom week number for Google Calendar.

How to use? 
1. Install the extension 
2. Click the extension icon 
3. Enter first date of first week in the pop-up and click set (if nothing happens, refresh page and try again)


Features coming soon:
1. Add support for more views (currently only supports viewing by month and week)

Report a bug / request for more features via email in the details section below. 
Alternatively, you can report bugs under the user support section below.
Please leave a review if you are enjoying this extension, thanks!

Thanks for installing this extension.
